I suddenly hear the sound of swallowing

I lower my gaze to the man's thing in the
video.

than that...)

The thing that I had stared at countless
times overlaps with the one in the
video. And within me, a conviction was
born that the thing on that wax figure
was made to resemble this.

so, why would he give me something like
this...)

I don't understand... No, it's probably
pointless to even think about it. Our
genders are different, our ages are
different... and our ways of thinking
and the environments we grew up in are
different too.

Above all else... I, who have led a biased
life prioritizing my music activities,
cannot comprehend it.
